  "prompt": "Where do you get the best cakes in pune?",
  "response": "Pune has a plethora of bakeries and patisseries that offer a wide selection of delicious cakes. Some of the popular places known for their cakes in Pune include:\n\n1. **Kayani Bakery:** Famous for their Shrewsbury biscuits, Kayani also offers delectable cakes.\n2. **German Bakery:** Known for its flavorful cakes and pastries with options for both vegetarian and non-vegetarian preferences.\n3. **Baked and Wired:** A trendy spot with a wide variety of cakes and desserts.\n4. **ABC Farms:** Although they are best known for their cheese, their bakery section offers some delightful cakes.\n5. **The French Window Patisserie:** Offers a range of classic French cakes and pastries in a cozy setting.\n6. **Forennte Patisserie:** Known for their elegant and tasty cakes and desserts.\n7. **Copper Chocs:** A popular chain with a wide range of cake options.\n8. **Just Baked:** Offers customized cakes along with regular favorites.\n\nEach of these places has its unique flavor and specialty, ensuring that you\u2019re likely to find the best cake based on your personal preferences.",
